snippet.title: Myst of Guatemala: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Myst of Guatemala 
On steam:https://store.steampowered.com/app/3094220/?utm_source=youtube  
or 
On Yahaha:https://yahaha-horror.itch.io/myst-of-guatemala

Inspired by the real historical event: The Guatemala Syphilis Experiment. In the 1940s to 1970s, the US government conducted unethical syphilis experiments on unsuspecting Guatemalans, causing severe physical and mental trauma, and sparking ethical and legal controversies.
